The function "Diag UDS Processing" shall «provide the adaption 'TLT-Slave' (DID 0x0BA9) via service "WriteDataByIdentifierRequest[]" regarding allowed Value Range, Diagnostic Session ID and Security Level  ('PH_Anpassungen_VW_02')  as follows:
/* Lap time */
	-set "Diag_TLTSlaveLapTimeInfo" := "WriteDataByIdentifierRequest[TrustworthyLocalTimeSlavePerformanceAdaption.LapTime]"
/* Response time */
	-set "Diag_TLTSlaveResponseTimeInfo" := "WriteDataByIdentifierRequest[TrustworthyLocalTimeSlavePerformanceAdaption.ResponseTime]"
/* slave id */
	-set "Diag_TLTSlaveSlaveIdInfo" := "WriteDataByIdentifierRequest[TrustworthyLocalTimeSlavePerformanceAdaption.SlaveId]".
	-set "Diag_TLTRequest" := 'set tlt adaptions',
	-send request to 'TLT' TrustworthyLocalTimeSlave.
».
